Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:16.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I begin my weekends by feeding the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I go jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burnable trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recyclable trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:40.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I go home to shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:47.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, I normally clean and have breakfast, and then I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:55.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan are coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:08.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are coming over today, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:12.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad will get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:28.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'s-sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:34.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're Sawako's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:38.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one seems to be pretty normal, though she's got a lot of makeup on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:39.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her classmate, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How many piercings does she have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan, Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, I was baking a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homemade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I brought some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:10.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have made something savory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like homemade cake more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat as much as you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, you'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:24.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well well, don't just stand at the door, do come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:33.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two please have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:36.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:39.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano Ayane-chan and Yoshida Chizuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:41.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to finally meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to finally meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She saved her from bombing a class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:57.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your room's actually pretty colorful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:10.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured no one would be bothered if my room suits me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously over-thinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:17.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:28.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking through pictures of the trip, and you were in these ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.58,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure there are no ghosts in these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect then. Here, a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they don't look creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look through them more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I do something so rude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin sneaked that picture of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, right? You look like a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I must have been heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:24.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, as much of a loser as he is, it'd be sad if he couldn't hold up one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya caught on in that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:38.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, I have so many treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so content with just pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go confess already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To who? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Kazehaya, your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To go out with him, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:17.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't, and besides, I'm already overwhelmed as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine going any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:26.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep saying that. What if someone takes Kazehaya away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could be happy for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could congratulate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:43.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you wouldn't want to go out with someone right away just because you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rented these yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear god no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru's so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like animals, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:39.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Fourteen calls, all from Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ringing for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:49.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain in the ass, so I figured, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.16,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have things to do too, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Kuronuma here, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I can't stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into Kuronuma last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing research too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, research.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Research?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adult videos, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:51.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Documentaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:02.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He sounds a bit nasal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.10,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:12.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, be sure to wash your hands and gargle with salt water when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prevention's the best cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she want me to cleanse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:29.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got home and forgot all about her warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could figure out is that he rented porn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:46.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but he sounded weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to bring Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:55.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Chizuru said she's going to Kuronuma's place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'd want to see Maru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sawako okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't become a bad girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, five cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:17.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She bought enough for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:29.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're telling ghost stories in there, so I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave those there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me wash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so awesome at washing dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, so fast, so clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm trying to show off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's got her dad's brows, eyes and nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her mom's profile and mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both nice girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah sure, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru's here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:36.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin's sick or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go to his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:08.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's too late for gargling if you're already in the nasal stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Maru wants to see you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you have said you wanted to see her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:48.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And I even get to meet Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:05.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:20.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay in your blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:33.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To banish the spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.45,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:55.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I acting like his boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think I'm okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this room okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you growling at, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:13.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this scratching sound yesterday night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hearing things because of the fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine, please just get some rest and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:24.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your room might take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A purification, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I like cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:40.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to tell you a story until you fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:42.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}just{\i0} heard this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This actually happened in this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man lived alone in an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He heard knocking every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:03.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He opens the door, but there's no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:07.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, in that apartment, in that very room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sleeps pretty well for someone who just freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazehaya-kun when he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've infringed on your privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:42.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm crying because I lost in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin laughed at me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, aren't you going to play with Maru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get in Sanada-kun's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should go play with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, just go out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sleeps so peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The medication kicked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room smells different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you next time I'm haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, pesky brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if there's anything you want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:55.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Shouta and Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come talk to me and I'll tell you their soft spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:02.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They better not be talking smack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it out when you want to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll love it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:23.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome, I feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's cake was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:57.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ended sort of weird, but I'll come over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:59.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:05.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of don't want to part, since we were together all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:14.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longer we're together, the harder it is to say bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:19.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk her home, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really dark, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:32.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, I'll be careful not to scare anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:33.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if you don't want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:56.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:00.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to your folks for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't I want him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The days are getting shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.41,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank him, but I can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:25.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai-sensei told me to hold on to you and close my eyes for five seconds when I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, if you do that again, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hear his voice so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and if I'm with him so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and if I see him so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:04.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I can't stand parting with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:08.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:17.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll feel like telling him how I feel someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrival of winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the footsteps of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:38.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Chizuru's Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:41.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
